{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/blog/how-to-bring-together-university-and-work","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>How did it start?</h2>\n<p>I’ve started my adventure at Bright Inventions from a three month summer Internship, but now it’s time to go back to the university. It has got a little bit complicated when it turned out that I have to be in two places at the same time - I have tried bilocation, but unfortunately failed… And sometimes I need to sleep, so even trilocation is wanted.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a71ed4f52ae35e20527484a5dd485932/7cc5e/wanted.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 150%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"wantedImage\"\n        title=\"wantedImage\"\n        src=\"/static/a71ed4f52ae35e20527484a5dd485932/7cc5e/wanted.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a71ed4f52ae35e20527484a5dd485932/a80bd/wanted.jpg 148w,\n/static/a71ed4f52ae35e20527484a5dd485932/1c91a/wanted.jpg 295w,\n/static/a71ed4f52ae35e20527484a5dd485932/7cc5e/wanted.jpg 480w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>{: .center-image}</p>\n<h2>Typical day</h2>\n<p>Staying focused during lectures or laboratories requires a huge amount of energy (which can be sometimes replaced with a particular amount of coffee). But it’s getting even harder when you get a few hours of work, instead of a few hours of sleep.</p>\n<p>One thing is needed to bring these things together - a positive attitude. Tell your brain that your work/study time is, in fact,  your spare time - you do what you like, so it’s not going to make you tired. That’s not all - your free time is also between the lectures and the time when you go from the university to work etc. You can dedicate this time to reading books or whatever you like. It should be just something that relaxes you. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8e47866b79fb9e4fbbbd57d5d403411c/6a068/relax.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"relaxImage\"\n        title=\"relaxImage\"\n        src=\"/static/8e47866b79fb9e4fbbbd57d5d403411c/1c72d/relax.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8e47866b79fb9e4fbbbd57d5d403411c/a80bd/relax.jpg 148w,\n/static/8e47866b79fb9e4fbbbd57d5d403411c/1c91a/relax.jpg 295w,\n/static/8e47866b79fb9e4fbbbd57d5d403411c/1c72d/relax.jpg 590w,\n/static/8e47866b79fb9e4fbbbd57d5d403411c/a8a14/relax.jpg 885w,\n/static/8e47866b79fb9e4fbbbd57d5d403411c/6a068/relax.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>{: .center-image}</p>\n<h2>To sleep, or not to sleep?</h2>\n<p>And here comes the most important moment - you are coming back home. And what now? No one will tell you what to do. There are many things that need to be done now. I suggest writing them down and putting/hanging in a place which you see all the time - for example, I use my week plan as a wallpaper in my notebook.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Make and eat supper.</li>\n<li>Start new project.</li>\n<li>Tidy your room.</li>\n<li>Study for next laboratories, etc.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Ups, you did half of the planned things and look at the clock and it’s midnight and... your first lecture starts at 8 a.m.. In theory people need 8 hours of sleep every day to stay healthy, but students know that it’s a lie. :)  When you get 5 hours of sleep a day, you get an incredible ability to fall asleep under any circumstances, at any time, and in any position. So, five hours is really a lot. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/738bd410ba111f291f20ac30629c9b26/6a068/sleep.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.83783783783784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sleepImage\"\n        title=\"sleepImage\"\n        src=\"/static/738bd410ba111f291f20ac30629c9b26/1c72d/sleep.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/738bd410ba111f291f20ac30629c9b26/a80bd/sleep.jpg 148w,\n/static/738bd410ba111f291f20ac30629c9b26/1c91a/sleep.jpg 295w,\n/static/738bd410ba111f291f20ac30629c9b26/1c72d/sleep.jpg 590w,\n/static/738bd410ba111f291f20ac30629c9b26/a8a14/sleep.jpg 885w,\n/static/738bd410ba111f291f20ac30629c9b26/6a068/sleep.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>{: .center-image}</p>\n<h2>Last, but not least...</h2>\n<p>To stay healthy in mind you shouldn’t forget about your family and friends (if you still have any ;) - write or call someone every day, try not to be antisocial and devote at least half an hour of your daily time for other people.\nAnd my last question is - how good are you at maths? Because I think all this leads us to an interesting mathematical paradox - day consists of 24 hours, but sometimes it’s possible to count them up to 30.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cd4b1c7939b185a660338d0271c60054/80e3c/time.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"timeImage\"\n        title=\"timeImage\"\n        src=\"/static/cd4b1c7939b185a660338d0271c60054/1c72d/time.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cd4b1c7939b185a660338d0271c60054/a80bd/time.jpg 148w,\n/static/cd4b1c7939b185a660338d0271c60054/1c91a/time.jpg 295w,\n/static/cd4b1c7939b185a660338d0271c60054/1c72d/time.jpg 590w,\n/static/cd4b1c7939b185a660338d0271c60054/80e3c/time.jpg 720w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>{: .center-image}</p>\n<p>I encourage everyone to be a student in some way - stay focused, be proud of what you do and use well all 48 hours of your each day. </p>","excerpt":"How did it start? I’ve started my adventure at Bright Inventions from a three month summer Internship, but now it’s time to go back to the…","frontmatter":{"slug":null,"title":"How to bring together university and work?","description":null,"author":"grzesiek","tags":["work","university","time-management"],"date":"2017-10-12T22:00:00.000Z","image":null},"timeToRead":2,"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/new-www/new-www/src/mdData/blog/2017-10-13-how-to-bring-together-university-and-work.md"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://brightinventions.pl"}}},"pageContext":{"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/new-www/new-www/src/mdData/blog/2017-10-13-how-to-bring-together-university-and-work.md"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2189233960","3181594896"]}